      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2095519390630161858, guid: 57f514415421ee6478317c4896764578, type: 3}
      propertyPath: noteContent
      value: 'The landscape was a lie. Just dead paint hiding the rot.

        But
        the true illusion sits in plain sight. Seek the hollow box with the black
        glass eye. It stares without seeing, dreaming of static and severed voices.

        Turn
        the dial. Let the white noise bleed.'
